%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20AI%20data%20center%20boom%20is%20moving%20closer%20to%20cities%20%E2%80%94%20and%20this%20Texas%20developer%20just%20raised%20%242%20billion%20to%20bet%20on%20it%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226488%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Stargate%20AI%20data%20center%20under%20construction%20in%20Abilene%2C%20Texas%2C%20US%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e6a182a98bc8fdc096cabd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224203%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETexas%20is%20becoming%20a%20hot%20spot%20for%20AI%20data%20centers%2C%20including%20mega-campuses%20like%20Stargate%20in%20Abilene.%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20Dallas-based%20data%20center%20developer%20secured%20%242%20billion%20for%20a%20data%20center%20project.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20AI%20boom%20is%20shifting%20toward%20facilities%20closer%20to%20users%2C%20not%20just%20remote%20mega%20campuses.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDemand%20for%20AI%20compute%20is%20surging%2C%20but%20the%20project%20had%20to%20navigate%20cautious%20lenders.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETexas%20has%20become%20a%20hot%20spot%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftexas-data-centers-virginia-top-market-status-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejumbo-sized%20data%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20far-flung%20locations%20that%20provide%20the%20heavy%20computing%20for%20artificial%20intelligence%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20phase%20of%20the%20AI%20boom%20is%20taking%20shape%20closer%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-center-locations-us-map-ai-boom-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewhere%20people%20live.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDataBank%2C%20a%20Dallas-based%20data%20center%20developer%20and%20operator%2C%20is%20capitalizing%20on%20growing%20demand%20for%20facilities%20built%20closer%20to%20population%20hubs%2C%20where%20they%20can%20deliver%20AI%20models%20to%20users%20more%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20it%20has%20secured%20%242%20billion%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpower-players-data-center-debt-boom-goldman-apollo-smbc-kkr-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econstruction%20financing%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20a%20group%20of%20banks%20led%20by%20Mitsubishi%20UFJ%20Financial%20Group%20to%20construct%20three%20data%20center%20buildings%20in%20Red%20Oak%2C%20a%20suburb%2020%20miles%20outside%20Dallas.%20DataBank%20did%20not%20disclose%20the%20other%20banks%20involved%20in%20extending%20the%20loan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMUFG%20is%20also%20leading%20a%20separate%2C%20ongoing%20effort%20to%20raise%20roughly%20another%20%24600%20million%20loan%20for%20a%20fourth%20building%20that%20will%20be%20part%20of%20the%20Red%20Oak%20campus.%20That%20debt%20will%20be%20sourced%20from%20the%20private%20placement%20market%2C%20tapping%20capital%20from%20Wall%20Street%20investors%2C%20according%20to%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20four-building%20cluster%2C%20which%20together%20will%20total%20240%20megawatts%20of%20computing%20capacity%2C%20has%20been%20leased%20by%20a%20hyperscaler%2C%20according%20to%20Raul%20Martynek%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20DataBank%2C%20who%20declined%20to%20name%20the%20tenant%2C%20saying%20only%20that%20it%20was%20one%20of%20the%20major%20hyperscalers%2C%20listing%20Amazon%2C%20Google%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20Oracle%2C%20or%20Meta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMajor%20technology%20companies%20have%20focused%20on%20building%20immense%20facilities%20with%20the%20computing%20power%20to%20develop%20advanced%20AI%20models.%20Martynek%20said%20the%20success%20of%20DataBank's%20Red%20Oak%20project%20reflects%20the%20increasing%20demand%20for%20so-called%20inference%20facilities%20that%20offer%20the%20physical%20proximity%20and%20networking%20speeds%20to%20allow%20customers%20to%20use%20and%20interact%20with%20AI%20seamlessly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20do%20data%20center%20users%20want%20to%20be%20close%20to%20metro%20markets%3F%20Because%20that's%20where%20most%20of%20the%20fiber%20is%20and%20that's%20where%20people%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20Martynek%20said.%20%26quot%3BWho%20consumes%20these%20products%3F%20People.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInference%20computing%2C%20which%20handles%20the%20work%20of%20processing%20a%20prompt%20when%20it%20is%20entered%20into%20an%20AI%20model%2C%20is%20a%20fast-growing%20segment%20of%20the%20data%20center%20market.%20In%202025%2C%209%25%20of%20data%20center%20workloads%20were%20for%20inference%20computing%20versus%2014%25%20for%20training%2C%20according%20to%20global%20data%20from%20JLL.%20The%20remaining%2077%25%20was%20used%20for%20traditional%20data%20center%20cloud%20computing.%20By%202030%2C%20JLL%20predicts%20that%2037%25%20of%20the%20data%20center%20industry's%20workloads%20will%20be%20for%20inference%20computing%20and%2013%25%20will%20be%20for%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20on%20the%20forefront%20of%20a%20lot%20of%20minds%2C%26quot%3B%20Carl%20Beardsley%2C%20head%20of%20data%20centers%20for%20JLL%20Capital%20Markets%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20next%20phase%20is%20once%20your%20models%20have%20learned%2C%20and%20they've%20trained%20up%2C%20to%20convert%20that%20over%20to%20inference%20and%20be%20closer%20to%20the%20population%20center.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fe930eaf-1e81-4de3-b5e2-9eacba82af77%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELenders%20are%20wary%20despite%20surging%20AI%20demand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20surging%20demand%20for%20AI%20computing%2C%20lenders%20have%20also%20grown%20wary%20in%20recent%20months%20about%20accruing%20enormous%20debts%20tied%20to%20a%20handful%20of%20major%20AI%20and%20data%20center%20players.%20In%20January%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foracle-openai-stargate-loans-jpmorgan-diminishing-interest-debt-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%20reported%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20JPMorgan%20Chase%20and%20MUFG%20encountered%20headwinds%20as%20they%20sought%20to%20sell%20off%20pieces%20of%20%2438%20billion%20in%20debt%20tied%20to%20two%20large%20data%20center%20campuses%20that%20will%20be%20occupied%20by%20Oracle.%20The%20two%20banks%20had%20extended%20loans%20to%20the%20projects%20with%20a%20group%20of%20other%20lenders%20in%20a%20process%20known%20as%20syndication%2C%20which%20allows%20lenders%20to%20share%20risks%20and%20the%20immense%20costs%20of%20large-scale%20financing%20packages%20by%20pooling%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMartynek%20acknowledged%20that%20the%20syndication%20market%20had%20slowed%20as%20DataBank%20sought%20financing%20for%20its%20Red%20Oak%20project.%20Martynek%20said%20that%20was%20why%20the%20loan%20for%20the%20fourth%20data%20center%20building%20was%20ultimately%20broken%20off%20from%20the%20syndication%20effort%20and%20will%20be%20sourced%20through%20a%20private%20placement%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20took%20us%20longer%20than%20we%20originally%20anticipated%20because%20obviously%20we're%20part%20of%20the%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20Martynek%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20a%20major%20money%20center%20bank%20says%2C%20'Hey%2C%20you%20know%20what%3F%20We're%20going%20to%20slow%20down%20the%20amount%20of%20credit%20that%20we're%20going%20to%20provide%20to%20this%20sector%20just%20because%20there's%20so%20much%20of%20it%2C'%20we're%20going%20to%20be%20impacted%20by%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20buildings%20comprise%20half%20of%20the%208-building%2C%20480-megawatt%20data%20center%20campus%20that%20DataBank%20plans%20to%20eventually%20erect%20in%20Red%20Oak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMartynek%20said%20that%20DataBank%20expects%20to%20deliver%20the%20first%20of%20the%20four%20initial%20buildings%20in%20the%20third%20quarter%20of%202026%20and%20the%20last%20by%20the%20end%20of%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdatabank-financing-dallas-data-center-inference-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776765301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e6a1d13fecbb42897a1e37%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdatabank-financing-dallas-data-center-inference-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Data%20center%20development%20has%20focused%20on%20massive%20projects%20for%20AI%20training%20in%20obscure%20locations.%20AI%20inference%20is%20pushing%20construction%20closer%20to%20cities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22dgeiger%40businessinsider.com%20(Daniel%20Geiger)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdatabank-financing-dallas-data-center-inference-2026-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Take%20my%20breadth%20away%3A%20What%20a%20historically%20top-heavy%20stock%20market%20means%20for%20investors%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22nyse%20chart%204-20-26%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e690f8367066d7c296ec7d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Nagle%2FBloomberg%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMarket%20breadth%2C%20which%20measures%20how%20many%20stocks%20are%20participating%20in%20a%20move%2C%20is%20at%20a%20multi-year%20low.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20recent%20surge%20to%20record%20highs%20has%20been%20driven%20by%20a%20small%20group%20of%20companies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhether%20that's%20good%20or%20bad%20for%20investors%20depends%20on%20the%20factors%20detailed%20below.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAnyone%20who's%20done%20a%20group%20project%20in%20school%20knows%20the%20usual%20dynamic%3A%20A%20couple%20of%20overachievers%20drive%20the%20bus%2C%20while%20other%2C%20more%20passive%20team%20members%20hitch%20a%20ride.%20Everyone%20gets%20the%20same%20grade.%20The%20division%20of%20labor%20is%20unspoken%20and%20largely%20accepted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20dynamic%20has%20played%20out%20in%20the%20stock%20market%20in%20recent%20years.%20In%20this%20analogy%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks-to-buy-ai-mag-7-nvidia-microsoft-google-amazon-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMagnificent%207%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20the%20overachievers.%20And%20while%20stock%20returns%20were%20starting%20to%20broaden%20to%20other%20sectors%20before%20the%20Iran%20war%2C%20the%20market's%20recent%20V-shaped%20jag%20has%20restored%20the%20market%20to%20default%20settings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chart%20below%20shows%20this%20breadth%20reduction%20in%20action.%20Since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Iran%20war%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fs%26amp%3Bp_500%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20outperformed%20its%20equal-weighted%20counterpart%2C%20and%20the%20Mag%207%20has%20blown%20away%20both%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FkE4bu%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Line%20chart%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FkE4bu%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20don't%20just%20take%20my%20word%20for%20it.%20New%20data%20from%20Goldman%20Sachs%20finds%20that%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20breadth%20is%20at%20its%20lowest%20level%20since%20mid-2023.%20Some%20additional%20stats%20that%20show%20how%20narrow%20the%20stock%20market's%20rally%20off%20lows%20has%20been%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20information%20technology%20and%20communication%20services%20sectors%20in%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20have%20accounted%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bus