il%20Nagesh%20Bhat's%20action%20film%20shifts%20from%20Lakhan%20to%20Parshuram%2C%20better%20suiting%20its%20epic%20scale.%20Shooting%20starts%20October%3B%20official%20announcement%20soon.%20Deol's%20slate%3A%20Gabru%2C%20Lahore%201947%20(Aug%202026%2C%20Aamir%20Khan%20prod.)%2C%20and%20Nitesh%20Tiwari's%20Ramayana.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20a%20Bank%20of%20America%20exec%20who%20once%20got%20passed%20over%20for%20a%20promotion.%20Here's%20what%20it%20taught%20me.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221856%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bernard%20Hampton%2C%20Bank%20of%20America%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69dd4f9a899c9d3be051025f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221392%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBernard%20Hampton%20is%20head%20of%20The%20Academy%20at%20Bank%20of%20America.%3Cp%3EBank%20of%20America%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBernard%20Hampton%2C%20head%20of%20The%20Academy%20at%20Bank%20of%20America%2C%20reflects%20on%20a%20time%20he%20didn't%20get%20a%20promotion.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20it%20taught%20him%20to%20better%20share%20his%20accomplishments%20and%20be%20more%20intentional%20in%20one-on-ones.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHampton%20said%20the%20experience%20also%20taught%20him%20to%20take%20ownership%20of%20his%20role%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Bernard%20Hampton%2C%20managing%20director%20and%20head%20of%20Bank%20of%20America's%20learning%20and%20skill%20development%20organization%2C%20The%20Academy.%20He's%20based%20in%20Fort%20Lauderdale.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20learn%20from%20disappointment%20in%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20once%20a%20time%2C%20around%202010%2C%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fex-amazon-vp-explains-simplest-way-to-get-promoted-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EI%20didn't%20get%20a%20role.%3C%2Fa%3E%20A%20key%20quality%20for%20the%20role%20was%20leaders%20who%20were%20helping%20peers%20elevate%20their%20performance%2C%20beyond%20leading%20high-performing%20teams.%20Ultimately%2C%20I%20didn't%20get%20it%20because%20I%20made%20assumptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-companies-employees-prove-productivity-rto-performance-reviews-ai-investments-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EI%20assumed%20my%20leader%20knew%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20I%20stood%20up%20a%20weekly%20routine%2C%20bringing%20my%20colleagues%20together%20as%20a%20peer%20group.%20They%20were%20also%20unaware%20of%20the%20colleagues%20I%20mentored%20in%20each%20division%20across%20the%20country%20each%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20activities%20weren't%20something%20I%20shared%20in%20one-on-ones.%20My%20leader%20typically%20talked%20about%20performance%20and%20business%20planning%2C%20so%20that's%20what%20I%20talked%20about%2C%20and%20I%20missed%20an%20opportunity%20to%20expand%20the%20view%20of%20my%20value%20to%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20disappointing%2C%20it%20allowed%20me%20to%20reorient.%20It%20also%20gave%20me%20an%20opportunity%20to%20be%20clearer%20and%20build%20better%20relationships%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20with%20my%20leader%2C%20but%20with%20other%20leaders%20at%20their%20level%2C%20and%20even%20the%20leader%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFortunately%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20take%20the%20role%20a%20year%20later.%20But%20without%20that%20disappointment%2C%20there%20could%20have%20been%20a%20real%20miss%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20Here's%20what%20the%20experience%20taught%20me%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224529d895-4290-435d-bd96-eedcfa31ac68%5C%22%3ERoutines%20matter%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFeedback%20shouldn't%20feel%20like%20it's%20coming%20out%20of%20left%20field.%20Ideally%2C%20you%20get%20formalized%20one-on-one%20coaching%20through%20regular%20check-ins%20or%20performance%20assessments.%20So%20I%20learned%20to%20better%20use%20my%20one-on-ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReputations%20are%20formed%20through%20consistency%2C%20and%20these%20kinds%20of%20conversations%2C%20depending%20on%20level%2C%20should%20take%20place%20consistently%20two%20to%20four%20times%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it's%20time%20for%20a%20six-month%20or%2090-day%20review%2C%20I%20make%20note%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-do-end-year-prepare-for-2026-work-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereally%20important%20milestones%20in%20my%20work%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20includes%20things%20that%20underscore%20the%20value%20I%20bring%20to%20the%20organization%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20ways%20I%20showed%20up%20throughout%20the%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20the%20time%20to%20paint%20the%20full%20picture%2C%20and%20that%20composite%20view%20can%20be%20really%20powerful%20when%20summarized%20in%20the%20right%20way%20of%20what%20it's%20meant%20for%20your%20skill%20development%2C%20what%20it's%20meant%20in%20contribution%20to%20the%20organization%2C%20and%20how%20it%20impacts%20the%20organization%20or%20line%20of%20business%20that%20you%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aebef9e7-c7be-4811-aafb-c64dc50bb2fa%5C%22%3EDon't%20make%20snap%20judgments%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDisappointments%2C%20mistakes%2C%20and%20challenges%20are%20part%20of%20life%20and%20careers.%20When%20they%20happen%20professionally%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20recognize%20that%20I%20joined%20the%20right%20company%2C%20with%20a%20culture%20and%20values%20that%20I%20believe%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToo%20often%2C%20people%20make%20snap%20judgments.%20If%20you%20think%20favorably%20of%20those%20parts%20of%20the%20company%2C%20then%2C%20in%20moments%20of%20disappointment%2C%20the%20key%20question%20is%3A%20%26quot%3BWhere%20did%20this%20go%20wrong%3F%20What%20was%20my%20share%20of%20it%3F%20Am%20I%20just%20blaming%20the%20company%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20find%20that%20much%20more%20can%20be%20understood%20about%20one's%20reaction%20to%20adversity%20over%20the%20much%20easier%20circumstance%20of%20when%20every%20day%20is%20roses.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOur%20best%20efforts%20come%20down%20to%20asking%20for%20feedback%2C%20and%20being%20very%20open%20to%20feedback%20and%20questioning%20if%20we%20have%20done%20our%20best%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228df68313-2fb2-4eac-a28b-62d3a9457a6d%5C%22%3EHave%20confidence%20and%20humility%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20moments%20of%20feedback%2C%20it's%20easy%20to%20lack%20confidence.%20I'm%20a%20high-functioning%20introvert%2C%20and%20it's%20easy%20to%20feel%20like%20I%20can't%20ask%20the%20important%20question.%20Even%20in%20disappointing%20situations%2C%20you%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20ask%20what%20made%20the%20difference%20and%20where%20you%20could%20have%20been%20stronger.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-5-reasons-employees-denied-raises-promotions-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epeople%20who%20continually%20ask%20for%20feedback%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20take%20action%20on%20it%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20build%20credibility%20and%20career%20confidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mom%20used%20to%20say%20to%20my%20two%20siblings%20and%20me%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20no%20better%20than%20anyone%20else%2C%20but%20no%20one%20else%20is%20better%20than%20you.%26quot%3B%20It%20was%20burned%20into%20my%20brain%20because%20it%20combines%20humility%20and%20confidence%20in%20one%20sentence.%20Humility%20keeps%20you%20learning%20and%20open%20to%20feedback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConfidence%20helps%20you%20take%20on%20stretch%20work%20and%20speak%20up.%20It%20keeps%20you%20going%2C%20even%20when%20you%20may%20be%20more%20junior.%20You%20need%20to%20engage%20with%20that%20feedback%2C%20and%20even%20more%20so%20in%20an%20era%20where%20the%20world%20is%20changing%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFeedback%20can%20be%20humbling%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20a%20weakness%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20the%20game.%20So%20being%20humble%20enough%20to%20learn%2C%20and%20confident%20enough%20to%20try%2C%20couldn't%20be%20more%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbank-of-america-exec-shares-lessons-learned-from-missing-promotion-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776763861000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69dd4fa5899c9d3be0510261%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbank-of-america-exec-shares-lessons-learned-from-missing-promotion-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bernard%20Hampton%2C%20head%20of%20The%20Academy%20at%20Bank%20of%20America%2C%20said%20missing%20out%20on%20a%20promotion%20taught%20him%20to%20have%20a%20routine%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20one-on-ones.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aaltchek%40insider.com%20(Ana%20Altchek)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbank-of-america-exec-shares-lessons-learned-from-missing-promotion-2026-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gabriel%20Byrne%20and%20Geraldine%20James%20to%20Star%20in%20World%20Stage%20Premiere%20of%20%E2%80%9945%20Years%E2%80%99%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776763800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236726642%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gabriel%20Byrne%20and%20Geraldine%20James%20will%20lead%20the%20world%20stage%20premiere%20of%20%E2%80%9C45%20Years%2C%E2%80%9D%20Hannah%20Patterson%E2%80%99s%20theatrical%20adaptation%20of%20Andrew%20Haigh%E2%80%99s%202015%20film%2C%20directed%20by%20Prasanna%20Puwanarajah%2C%20at%20the%20Minerva%20Theatre%2C%20Chic