g%20in%20utilities%2C%20materials%2C%20and%20industrials%20for%20exposure%20to%20the%20theme.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhere-to-invest-now-tech-stocks-buy-the-dip-goldman-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETech%20stocks%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20regained%20favor%20among%20investors%20over%20the%20last%20month%2C%20after%20a%20sell-off%20brought%20the%20sector's%20valuations%20down%20to%20historically%20cheap%20levels%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvesting-tips-buy-tech-stocks-ai-capex-hyperscalers-sp500-outlook-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EManish%20Kabra%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20sticking%20with%20physical%20assets.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoci%C3%A9t%C3%A9%20G%C3%A9n%C3%A9rale's%20chief%20US%20equity%20strategist%20likes%20the%20picks%2C%20shovels%2C%20and%20hard%20materials%20of%20the%20world.%20In%20an%20interview%20with%20Business%20Insider%20last%20week%2C%20Kabra%20argued%20that%20the%20best%20investment%20opportunities%20right%20now%20are%20in%20commodities%20like%20metals%20and%20in%20stocks%20tied%20to%20demand%20for%20hard%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20view%20stems%20from%20a%20few%20trends.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20is%20the%20global%20trend%20of%20reshoring%20and%20reindustrialization%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20US%20and%20Europe%2C%20as%20countries%20move%20to%20secure%20their%20supply%20chains%20amid%20volatile%20trade%20policy%20and%20rising%20geopolitical%20tensions.%20Tied%20in%20with%20this%20is%20the%20ongoing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpower-players-data-center-debt-boom-goldman-apollo-smbc-kkr-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20buildout%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20data-center%20demand%20continues%20to%20rise%20globally%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecond%20is%20the%20rise%20in%20defense%20spending%20around%20the%20world%2C%20and%20the%20need%20for%20materials%20and%20metals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCurrently%208%25%20of%20corporate%20demand%20is%20coming%20from%20defense%20spending%2C%26quot%3B%20Kabra%20said.%20%26quot%3BWithin%20the%20Department%20of%20War%2C%20the%20two%20biggest%20commodities%20they%20buy%20are%20aluminum%20and%20copper.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20third%2C%20countries%20are%20increasingly%20building%20up%20strategic%20metal%20reserves%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLike%20how%20every%20country%20was%20focused%20and%20is%20focused%20on%20strategic%20reserves%20for%20oil%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20the%20strategic%20reserves%20for%20metals%20that's%20starting%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20pointed%20to%20the%20US%20adding%20copper%20and%20silver%20to%20its%20critical%20metals%20list%2C%20as%20well%20as%20to%20the%20European%20Union's%20announcement%20of%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsingle-market-economy.ec.europa.eu%2Fsectors%2Fraw-materials%2Fareas-specific-interest%2Fcritical-raw-materials%2Fcritical-raw-materials-act_en%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECritical%20Raw%20Materials%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKabra's%20outlook%20echoes%20the%20proponents%20of%20the%20so-called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-halo-trade-tech-rotation-iran-ai-wall-street-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHALO%20trade%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20short%20for%20%26quot%3Bheavy%20assets%2C%20low%20obsolescence%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20which%20has%20caught%20traction%20in%20recent%20months%20after%20asset-light%20companies%20in%20industries%20like%20software%20saw%20their%20shares%20rocked%20by%20threats%20of%20AI%20disruption.%20The%20thinking%20is%20that%20hard%20assets%20and%20firms%20that%20operate%20them%20will%20perform%20better%2C%20as%20companies%20need%20materials%20to%20develop%20AI%2C%20and%20these%20materials%20are%20not%20vulnerable%20to%20AI%20disruption%20in%20the%20same%20way%20as%20some%20tech%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22738fb5bf-5dc3-43e4-b861-69f7c56662bc%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20invest%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKabra%20shared%20a%20few%20ways%20investors%20can%20gain%20exposure%20to%20physical%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20is%20directly%20through%20market%20sectors%20like%20%3Cstrong%3Eutilities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%3Cstrong%3Ematerials%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cstrong%3Eindustrials%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20as%20they're%20all%20tied%20to%20the%20growing%20need%20for%20resources%20like%20metals%20and%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20others%20ways%20to%20gain%20heightened%20exposure%20to%20these%20assets%20is%20through%20%3Cstrong%3Ecertain%20broad%20stock%20indexes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20he%20said.%20Two%20that%20Kabra%20named%20are%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20equal-weighted%20index%20and%20the%20UK's%20FTSE%20100.%20The%20former%20has%20a%2032%25%20weighting%20to%20these%20sectors%20combined%20%E2%80%94%20much%20higher%20than%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20cap-weighted%20index%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20FTSE%20100%20has%20a%2040%25%20weighting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECertain%20%3Cstrong%3Ecurrencies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20also%20give%20indirect%20exposure%2C%20Kabra%20said%2C%20due%20to%20the%20resources%20in%20their%20respective%20countries.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20Australian%20dollar%20offers%20exposure%20to%20metals%20demand%3B%20the%20Canadian%20dollar%20and%20Norwegian%20Krona%20give%20exposure%20to%20energy%3B%20and%20the%20New%20Zealand%20dollar%20provides%20exposure%20to%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20Kabra%20said%20he%20likes%20metals%20themselves%2C%20like%3Cstrong%3E%20gold%20and%20copper%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20Societe%20Generale's%20ideal%20portfolio%20structure%20is%2050%25%20stocks%2C%2015%25%20commodities%2C%2025%25%20bonds%2C%20and%2010%25%20cash.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExamples%20of%20funds%20that%20offer%20stock-market%20exposure%20to%20the%20ideas%20above%20include%20the%20Invesco%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%C2%AE%20Equal%20Weight%20ETF%20(RSP)%2C%20Vanguard%20Materials%20ETF%20(VAW)%2C%20Fidelity%20MSCI%20Industrials%20Index%20ETF%20(FIDU)%2C%20iShares%20U.S.%20Utilities%20ETF%20(IDU)%2C%20SPDR%20Gold%20Shares%20(GLD)%2C%20and%20United%20States%20Copper%20Index%20Fund%20(CPER).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhere-to-invest-now-physical-assets-metals-industrials-materials-gold-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776763501000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e664f03fecbb42897a1bad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhere-to-invest-now-physical-assets-metals-industrials-materials-gold-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22SocGen%20says%20the%20best%20investment%20opportunities%20right%20now%20are%20in%20commodities%20like%20metals%20and%20in%20stocks%20tied%20to%20demand%20for%20hard%20assets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22wedwards%40businessinsider.com%20(William%20Edwards)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhere-to-invest-now-physical-assets-metals-industrials-materials-gold-2026-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Felt%20political%20pressure'%3A%20Sacked%20official%20blames%20Starmer%E2%80%99s%20office%20over%20Mandelson%20appointment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776763078000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-130413117%2Cimgsize-59196.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Ffelt-political-pressure-sacked-uk-official-blames-starmers-office-over-mandelson-us-appointment%2Farticleshow%2F130413042.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20WORLD%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Felt%20political%20pressure'%3A%20Sacked%20official%20blames%20Starmer%E2%80%99s%20offic