8%20against%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad.%20The%20franchise%20confirmed%20the%20batter%20requires%20six%20to%20twelve%20weeks%20of%20rehabilitation%2C%20ending%20his%20season.%20Mhatre%20continued%20batting%20after%20the%20initial%20injury%20before%20its%20severity%20was%20assessed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20moved%20to%20San%20Francisco%20to%20work%20in%20AI.%20Living%20here%20requires%20sacrifices%20%E2%80%94%20I%20gave%20up%20normalcy%20to%20gain%20access.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224742%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ahmed%20Ahres%20presenting%20on%20a%20stage%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69de9136d06bf1b90127397a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223163%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAhmed%20Ahres%20says%20living%20in%20San%20Francisco%20makes%20him%20feel%20like%20anything%20is%20possible.%3Cp%3EAhmed%20Ahres%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAhmed%20Ahres%20moved%20from%20London%20to%20San%20Francisco%20on%20an%20O-1%20Visa%20in%202025.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThough%20living%20in%20San%20Francisco%20has%20boosted%20his%20ambition%2C%20he%20has%20felt%20pressure%20to%20always%20be%20thriving.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAhres%20says%20it's%20difficult%20to%20escape%20talks%20about%20tech%2C%20but%20relationships%20are%20his%20key%20to%20boundaries.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Ahmed%20Ahres%2C%20a%2027-year-old%20Product%20%26amp%3B%20GTM%20at%20a%20tech%20startup%20based%20in%20San%20Francisco.%20It's%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20hold%20the%20belief%20that%20if%20you%20want%20to%20become%20the%20best%20in%20the%20world%20at%20something%2C%20you've%20got%20to%20surround%20yourself%20with%20the%20best%20in%20the%20world.%20For%20technology%2C%20the%20place%20to%20do%20that%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmake-most-money-tech-san-francisco-salary-sf-bay-area-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESan%20Francisco%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20moved%20here%20from%20London%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20I%20came%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-einstein-o1-visa-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20O-1%20visa%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20pathway%20for%20foreigners%20with%20exceptional%20abilities%20to%20live%20and%20work%20in%20the%20US.%20I%20came%20here%20willing%20to%20sacrifice%20things%20like%20closeness%20to%20my%20family%20in%20Tunisia%20because%20my%20priority%20is%20my%20tech%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20are%20you%20building%3F%26quot%3B%20is%20the%20first%20question%20someone%20might%20ask%20me%20if%20I%20stumble%20into%20a%20conversation%20at%20a%20bar%20or%20coffee%20shop%20here%20in%20San%20Francisco%3B%20not%20my%20name%2C%20or%20my%20job.%20Your%20career%20seems%20to%20matter%20more%20than%20who%20you%20are%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sheer%20amount%20of%20ambition%20and%20innovation%20in%20San%20Francisco%20is%20motivating%2C%20but%20this%20isn't%20an%20easy%20place%20to%20live%20in%20when%20your%20career%20is%20not%20thriving.%20Still%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20want%20to%20be%20anywhere%20else%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223878f25b-afa8-4251-9f90-12ca25646351%5C%22%3EI'm%20so%20much%20more%20ambitious%20in%20San%20Francisco%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20granted%20an%20O-1%20visa%20last%20year%20after%20raising%20funding%20from%20a%20US%20investor%20for%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-power-list%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20startup%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20visa%20lasts%20three%20years%2C%20and%20I%20can%20work%20in%20any%20job%20related%20to%20AI.%20Since%20moving%2C%20my%20cofounder%20has%20taken%20over%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20company%2C%20and%20I%20now%20work%20in%20product%20for%20a%20company%20building%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsc%2Fhow-generative-ai-is-transforming-production-for-brands-and-creators%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efuture%20of%20video%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20always%20been%20an%20ambitious%20person%2C%20but%20my%20level%20of%20ambition%20has%20increased%20massively%20since%20being%20surrounded%20by%20people%20who%20are%20basically%20telling%20me%2C%20whatever%20you're%20dreaming%2C%20you%20can%20dream%20of%20a%20vision%20that's%20one%20thousand%20times%20bigger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20feel%20like%20I%20can%20do%20things%20here.%20I%20had%20an%20idea%20to%20start%20a%20podcast%20in%20January%2C%20and%20a%20week%20later%2C%20I%20recorded%20my%20first%20episode.%20Our%20environment%20defines%20us%2C%20and%20seeing%20everyone%20here%20put%20things%20into%20action%20has%20inspired%20me%20to%20embody%20that%20same%20level%20of%20ambition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221604d6fa-3481-43db-8db0-a99be6516836%5C%22%3ESan%20Francisco%20feels%20like%20a%20place%20where%20anything%20is%20possible%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20see%20San%20Francisco%20as%20an%20environment%20that%20not%20only%20defines%20who%20I%20am%20today%2C%20but%20who%20I%20want%20to%20become%3A%20this%20ambitious%20person%20who%20can%20do%20anything%20he%20sets%20his%20mind%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-san-francisco-worth-it-cost-of-living-negativity-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESince%20being%20here%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20people%20have%20told%20me%2C%20%26quot%3BAhmed%2C%20you've%20become%20a%20bit%20crazy.%26quot%3B%20And%20I'm%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BYeah%2C%20I%20love%20it.%26quot%3B%20Being%20here%20makes%20me%20believe%20everything%20is%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20in%20a%20job%20where%20I'm%20thinking%20about%20how%20to%20increase%20revenue%20little%20by%20little.%20No%2C%20I%20want%20to%20do%20something%20that%20completely%20changes%20the%20world.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20just%20the%20nature%20of%20being%20surrounded%20by%20people%20who%20think%20like%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c5e91dde-f085-4415-affe-7aa4ae19c6ae%5C%22%3EThere's%20pressure%20to%20act%20like%20everything%20is%20OK%20all%20the%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20a%20transition%20period%20in%20late%202025%20when%20I%20knew%20I%20wanted%20to%20step%20back%20a%20little%20from%20the%20company%20I%20had%20built%3B%20I%20felt%20completely%20lost.%20In%20that%20time%2C%20I%20stopped%20going%20to%20events%20or%20even%20meeting%20up%20with%20people%20because%20I%20knew%20I'd%20get%20asked%20about%20what%20I%20was%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-startup-moving-into-smaller-neighborhoods-changing-office-culture-sf-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eexpectation%20in%20San%20Francisco%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20starting%20a%20company%20or%20doing%20something%20big%20at%20all%20times%2C%20so%20it%20was%20very%20hard%20to%20be%20open%20about%20my%20uncertainty.%20I%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20are%20pretending%20to%20be%20doing%20well%20out%20here%20when%20they're%20not.%20I%20did%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20certain%20dinners%20and%20events%2C%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20I%20was%20realizing%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20continue%20down%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flife-of-startup-founder-no-vc-funding-money-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emy%20path%20as%20a%20founder%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I'd%20often%20answer%20%26quot%3Bthe%20company%20is%20doing%20super%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BI'm%20excited%20about%20the%20future%26quot%3B%20when%20I%20wasn't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20hard%20being%20in%20a%20low%20place%20when%20it%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20the%20only%20one.%20Thankfully%2C%20I%20have%20a%20great%20support%20system%20around%20me.%20They%20were%20extremely%20supportive%20and%20encouraged%20me%20to%20pursue%20my%20passion%20and%20work%20on%20something%20that%20I%20absolutely%20love%20and%20believe%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f1cb6070-e964-4bd0-a7ec-1e1ea88bc97f%5C%22%3EIt's%20hard%20to%20escape%20conversations%20about%20technology%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20very%20passionate%20about%20technology%2C%20so%20I%20love%20talking%20about%20it%2C%20but%20there%20are%20times%20when%20I'm%20out%20doing%20something%20for%20fun%2C%20and%20I%20have%20to%20plainly%20say%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20talk%20about%20work.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-us-to-uk-surprising-challenges-years-later-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBack%20in%20London%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20people%20work%20hard%2C%20protect%20their%20personal%20time%2C%20and%20rarely%20talk%20about%20work%20outside%20of%20office%20hours.%20At%205%20p.m.%2C%20pubs%20and%20bars%20are%20full.%20The%20mentality%20is%20more%20%26quot%3Bwork%20to%20live%26quot%3B%20than%20%26quot%3Blive%20to%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20hard%20to%20escape%20talks%20about%20tech%2C%20but%20I'm%20lucky%20to%20have%20friends%20I%20already%20knew%20before%20moving%20and%20my%20brother%20here.%20I%20can%20have%20deep%20conversations%20with%20them%20about%20anything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20moved%2C%20I%20struggled%20to%20meet%20people%20outside%20of%20those%20few%2C%20but%20I've%20gotten%20into%20hobbies%20like%20tennis%2C%20where%20I've%20met%20some%20good%20friends%20who%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20work%2C%20and%20that%20has%20helped%20me%20settle%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d470adb6-e987-4c29-a340-3e54e54e01d0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBuilding%20genuine%20relationships%20is%20the%20key%20to%20boundaries%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsan-francisco-dating-apps-ai-matchmakers-technology-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESan%20Francisco%20tech%20scene%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20your%20status%20isn't%20defined%20by%20what%20car%20or%20home%20you%20own%3B%20it's%20defined%20by%20who%20you%20know%2C%20what%20you're%20building%2C%20and%20how%20much%20money%20you've%20raised.%20People%20really%20care%20about%20that%2C%20and%20it%20can%20be%20hard%20to%20make%20genuine%20relationships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20realized%20that%20it's%20OK%20to%20go%20to%20events%20and%20try%20to%20get%20customers%20and%20grow%20your%20company.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20it's%20very%20important%20that%20I%20create%2C%20build%2C%20and%20nurture%20relationships%20that%20are%20bigger%20than%20just%20work%20for%20my%20long-term%20happiness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaking%20sure%20I'm%20having%20deep%20conversations%20with%20friends%20about%20things%20outside%20of%20our%20jobs%20is%20really%20important%20to%20me%20and%20helps%20me%20find%20balance%20in%20my%20life%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20what%20it's%20like%20living%20in%20San%20Francisco%3F%20If%20so%2C%20please%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20reporter%20at%20tmartinelli%40businessinsider.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartup-founder-moved-to-san-francisco-feels-ambition-pressure-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776762661000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e135f0cb96e245212aef8a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartup-founder-moved-to-san-francisco-feels-ambition-pressure-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20startup%20founder%20who%20moved%20to%20San%20Francisco%20on%20an%20O-1%20Visa%20says%20his%20ambition%20has%20multiplied%2C%20but%20he%20feels%20pressure%20to%20always%20be%20thriving.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tmartinelli%40businessinsider.com%20(Tess%20Martinelli)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2