-founding-science-business-tech-solutions%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGen%20Z%20founders%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20launched%20into%20the%20business%20world%20with%20a%20bang%2C%20and%20legacy%20brands%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20keep%20up%20ever%20since.%20Just%20ask%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falinea-pitch-deck-gen-z-investing-seed-funding-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEve%20Halimi%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHalimi%20and%20Anam%20Lakhani%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falinea-pitch-deck-gen-z-investing-seed-funding-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecreated%20Alinea%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20investment%20platform%20designed%20for%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20wealth-builders%2C%20in%202021.%20The%20pair%20began%20building%20Alinea%20after%20interning%20on%20Wall%20Street%2C%20where%20one%20thing%20became%20crystal%20clear%3A%20the%20rich%20were%20getting%20richer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20richer%20were%20getting%20richer%20through%20the%20stock%20market%2C%20and%20people%20who%20didn't%20have%20the%20means%20weren't%20learning%20about%20it%20elsewhere%2C%26quot%3B%20Halimi%2C%2029%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWe%20saw%20this%20really%20big%20gap.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20uninitiated%2C%20learning%20to%20invest%20in%20the%20stock%20market%20can%20feel%20like%20a%20perplexing%20blur%20of%20hyper-specific%20jargon%2C%20oscillating%20graphs%2C%20and%20chasing%20after%20trends%20that%20may%20never%20pan%20out.%20Financially%20savvy%20folks%20have%20often%20relied%20on%20legacy%20institutions%20to%20manage%20their%20investments%20and%20assets%2C%20but%20not%20everyone%20has%20the%20know-how%20or%20access.%20That's%20where%20Alinea%20comes%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alinea%20Invest%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e6b6ae367066d7c296ee13%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221821%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlinea%20helps%20users%20build%20their%20wealth%20portfolios.%3Cp%3EAlinea%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20institutional%20players%20are%20moving%20too%20slow%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20advantage%20we%20have%20as%20a%20startup.%20We're%20able%20to%20move%20and%20innovate%20much%20faster.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20traditional%2C%20long-standing%20companies%20like%20JPMorgan%20had%20to%20adopt%20digital%20technology%20into%20their%20services%2C%20Alinea%20is%20part%20of%20the%20fintech%20wave%20built%20on%20it%20from%20the%20beginning.%20Alinea%20occupies%20the%20fintech%20space%20alongside%20companies%20like%20Robinhood%20and%20Coinbase%2C%20both%20of%20which%20went%20public%20in%202021%20after%20shaking%20up%20the%20finance%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20a%20relatively%20new%20company%2C%20Alinea%20has%20made%20serious%20strides.%20The%20company%20raised%20over%20%2410%20million%20in%20a%20funding%20round%20last%20year%20and%20received%20%2422.5%20million%20in%20user-acquisition%20funding%20from%20PvX%20Partners%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHalimi%20said%20that%20Alinea%2C%20compared%20to%20its%20Big%20Tech%20and%20fintech%20peers%2C%20has%20an%20edge%20in%20engaging%20new%20investors.%20The%20secret%20isn't%20glossy%20magazine%20ad%20campaigns%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuper-bowl-2026-advertisers-tech-glitches-salesforce-ai-kalshi-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESuper%20Bowl%20slots%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224303557c-ba5a-4f61-9d89-250e305303fa%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Hey%2C%20girls'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20true%20Gen%20Z%20fashion%2C%20Halimi%20and%20Lakhani%20struck%20gold%20on%20social%20media%2C%20growing%20their%20brand%20through%20TikTok%20videos.%20Halimi%20said%20they%20weave%20storytelling%20into%20their%20content%2C%20offering%20users%20glimpses%20of%20themselves%20and%20their%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20really%20resonated%20with%20us%20as%20founders%2C%20and%20talking%20about%20our%20own%20pain%20points%2C%26quot%3B%20Halimi%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20been%20our%20secret%20to%20topping%20the%20finance%20charts%20and%20getting%20all%20of%20these%20users%20with%20so%20little%20capital%20compared%20to%20all%20of%20these%20other%20companies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20look%20at%20the%20marketing%20landscape%20for%20consumer%20fintechs%2C%20you're%20never%20going%20to%20see%20the%20CEO%20of%20Vanguard%20get%20on%20TikTok%20and%20be%20like%2C%20'Hey%2C%20girls.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20cite%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40alineainvest%2Fvideo%2F7125602390169881902%5C%22%20data-video-id%3D%5C%227125602390169881902%5C%22%3E%20%3Csection%3E%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22%40alineainvest%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40alineainvest%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%40alineainvest%3C%2Fa%3E%20From%20a%20class%20project%20to%20a%20venture%20backed%20multi%20million%20dollar%20fintech%20startup%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22alineainvest%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ftag%2Falineainvest%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%23alineainvest%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22alineaapp%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ftag%2Falineaapp%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%23alineaapp%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22fintechfounders%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ftag%2Ffintechfounders%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%23fintechfounders%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22investingforfenz%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ftag%2Finvestingforfenz%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%23investingforfenz%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22nycstartup%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ftag%2Fnycstartup%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%23nycstartup%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22ycombinator%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ftag%2Fycombinator%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%23ycombinator%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22%E2%99%AC%20Canyons%20-%20Official%20Sound%20Studio%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Fmusic%2FCanyons-6681198633301314311%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%99%AC%20Canyons%20-%20Official%20Sound%20Studio%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fsection%3E%20%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20personable%20approach%20helped%20Alinea%20gain%20over%202.5%20million%20users.%20Initially%2C%20Halimi%20said%20their%20platform%20was%20geared%20toward%20Gen%20Z%20women%2C%20but%20that's%20changed%20over%20the%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20actually%20realized%20this%20market%20is%20way%20bigger%20than%20we%20expected.%20Last%20year%20our%20user%20base%20was%2092%25%20female%2C%20and%20now%20we're%2060%25%20female%2C%26quot%3B%20Halimi%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20because%20we're%20now%20getting%20men%20and%20all%20types%20of%20people%20who%20need%20this%20product.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20helps%20that%20Alinea%20is%20accessible%20at%20a%20time%20when%20investing%20has%20become%20popular%20with%20young%20people.%20A%20March%202025%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weforum.org%2Fpress%2F2025%2F03%2Fnew-research-finds-retail-investing-shift-towards-younger-investors-reshaping-market-trends%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAccording%2520to%2520a%2520survey%2520by%2520the%2520World%2C14%2525%2520of%2520Baby%2520Boomers%2520said%2520the%2520same%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWorld%20Economic%20Forum%20Survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20Gen%20Z%20begins%20investing%20earlier%20than%20previous%20generations.%20By%20the%20time%20Gen%20Z%20enters%20the%20workforce%2C%20over%2080%25%20will%20have%20learned%20about%20personal%20investing%2C%20compared%20with%2047%25%20of%20Baby%20Boomers%2C%20according%20to%20the%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20knows%20that%20they%20need%20to%20do%20it.%20Everyone%20is%20getting%20set%20up%20earlier.%20Everyone%20is%20investing%20more%20money%20in%20the%20stock%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20Halimi%20said.%20%26quot%3BWith%20the%20rise%20of%20social%20media%2C%20FinTok%20is%20popping.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2296a5f931-4afd-4920-adb0-8594b9cdf4b2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDigital%20natives%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGen%20Z%20has%20earned%20the%20title%20of%20digital%20natives%2C%20or%20a%20generation%20that%20grew%20up%20with%20advanced%20technology%20at%20their%20fingertips.%20As%20such%2C%20it's%20not%20a%20surprise%20that%20Alinea%20embraces%20tech%20like%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAllie%2C%20an%20AI-powered%20copilot%2C%20helps%20users%20navigate%20their%20first%20investments.%20Allie%20can%20provide%20market%20recaps%20and%20help%20users%20make%20informed%20investment%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe's%20going%20to%20ask%20you%20a%20few%20questions%20about%20yourself%2C%20like%20your%20risk%20tolerance%2C%20income%2C%20and%20what%20job%20you're%20doing.%20Based%20on%20that%2C%20she's%20going%20to%20give%20you%20a%20portfolio%20to%20invest%20in%20and%20recommend%20an%20amount%20you%20should%20invest%2C%26quot%3B%20Halimi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alinea's%20AI%20Allie%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e64a78367066d7c296e9e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222532%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlinea's%20AI%20Allie%3Cp%3EAlinea%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlinea%20also%20aims%20to%20connect%20with%20its%20users%20through%20features%20like%20Investment%20Playlists.%20The%20playlists%20are%20curated%20collections%20of%20stocks%20and%20ETFs%20tailored%20to%20a%20user's%20specific%20goal%20or%20theme.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlinea's%20wealth%20management%20service%20costs%20%24120%20a%20year%2C%20or%20%2410%20a%20month.%20The%20platform%20gives%20users%20access%20to%20stocks%2C%20ETFs%2C%20and%20cryptocurrencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20think%20about%20the%20day%20one%2C%20day%2018%2C%20day%2030%2C%20day%2060%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20Halimi%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20leveling%20them%20up%20on%20this%20journey%20and%20helping%20them%20gain%20that%20confidence%2C%20so%20even%20though%20they're%20beginners%20when%20they're%20getting%20started%2C%20they're%20pros%20by%20year%20one.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fgen-zalinea-founder-explains-how-to-connect-with-investors-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776762541000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e6b634367066d7c296ee0a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fgen-zalinea-founder-explains-how-to-connect-with-investors-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Eve%20Halimi%20and%20Anam%20Lakhani%20created%20Alinea%2C%20an%20investment%20platform%20designed%20for%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20wealth-builders%2C%20in%202021.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ledmonds%40businessinsider.com%20(Lauren%20Edmonds)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fgen-zalinea-founder-explains-how-to-connect-with-investors-2026-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22At%2049%2C%20I%20quit%20my%20lucrative%20tech%20job%20in%20Texas%20for%20a%20quieter%2C%20happier%20life%20in%20Tuscany.%20I%20lost%2042%20pounds%20in%20the%20process.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20in%20a%20red%20halter-neck%20dress%2C%20wearing%20sunglasses%20in%20Italy.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e28c5f3fecbb42897a1389%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAngie%20Smith%20left%20the%20rat%20race%20in%20Texas%20for%20Tuscany%20in%20the%20fall%20of%202023.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Angie%20Smith%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAngie%20Smith%20felt%20trapped%20in%20her%20corporate%20tech%20job.%20Her%20stress%20levels%20and%20overall%20health%20suffered.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20January%202023%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20leave%20her%20well-paid%20position%20in%20Texas%20and%20move%20to%20Italy%20that%20fall.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%2052-year-old%20enjoys%20a%20quieter%20life%2C%20runs%20retreats%20for%20women%2C%20and%20has%20gone%20down%20two%20dress%20sizes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20interview%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Angie%20Smith%2C%2052%2C%20a%20real%20estate%20advisor%20and%20founder%20of%20a%20women's%20retreat%20in%20Tuscany.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20time%20when%20I%20worked%20in%20tech%20sales%20in%20Fort%20Worth%2C%20Dallas%2C%20I%20was%20on%20the%20road%2C%20traveling%20across%20the%20Southern%20states.%20I'd%20stay%20in%20hotels%2C%20drink%20Margaritas%2C%20order%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaking-toddler-doordash-deliveries-helped-beat-homelessness-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efood%20on%20DoorDash%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20avoid%20exercising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20constantly%20sick%20with%20everything%20from%20digestive%20issues%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fmigraine-types%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emigraine%20headaches%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20eventually%20ended%20up%20in%20the%20hospital%20and%20went%20on%20anxiety%20medication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20put%20on%20weight%20and%2C%20at%205ft%207in%20tall%2C%20weighed%20218%20pounds%20at%20one%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20I%20was%20good%20at%20my%20job%2C%20which%20paid%20six%20figures%20annually%2C%20I'd%20get%20the%20%26quot%3BSunday%20Scaries%26quot%3B%20when%20the%20thought%20of%20yet%20another%20focus%20meeting%20the%20following%20morning%20filled%20me%20with%20dread.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2204e1d23d-24ed-4f29-9bdd-5d02cd5e21a8%5C%22%3EI'd%20always%20loved%20Italy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThings%20were%20so%20bad%20that%20my%20sister%20took%20me%20aside%20on%20several%20occasions%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAngie%2C%20if%20you%20don't%20change%20something%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20die.%26quot%3B%20We%20lost%20our%20brother%20suddenly%20in%202021%20at%2068.%20For%20years%2C%20he'd%20told%20me%2C%20%26quot%3BWork%20isn't%20everything.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202023%2C%20I%20finally%20took%20notice.%20I%20was%2049%2C%20and%20woke%20up%20one%20day%20thinking%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20heading%20into%20the%20second%20half%20of%20my%20life.%20Do%20I%20really%20want%20to%20keep%20on%20doing%20this%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-things-to-do-in-italy-from-couple-vacation-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eloved%20Italy%20%3C%2Fa%3Eever%20since%20spending%20two%20weeks%20there%20with%20my%20daughter%2C%20Taylor%2C%20when%20she%20graduated%20high%20school%20in%202013.%20We%20went%20to%20Milan%2C%20Rome%2C%20and%20Venice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20flight%20home%2C%20I%20cried%20because%20I%20felt%20such%20a%20connection%20to%20the%20place%20and%20the%20people.%20After%20that%2C%20I%20visited%20on%20vacation%20as%20often%20as%20I%20could.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side-by-side%20image%20of%20a%20woman%20with%20blond%20hair.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e66bc4367066d7c296ead0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESmith%2C%20pictured%20before%20and%20after%20her%20move%20to%20Italy.%20She%20said%20she%20looks%20and%20feels%20much%20healthier%20in%20Europe.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Angie%20Smith%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20had%20ideas%20about%20settling%20there%20before%2C%20which%20had%20come%20to%20nothing.%20But%20this%20time%2C%20after%20much%20thought%2C%20I%20was%20determined%20to%20make%20it%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20put%20in%20my%20notice%20in%20March%202023%20and%20left%20my%20job%20the%20following%20month.%20Then%20I%20put%20my%20home%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffort-worth-texas-cattle-drive-photos-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFort%20Worth%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20market%20for%20%24465%2C000.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Taylor%2C%20now%2031%2C%20who%20lives%20and%20works%20in%20London%2C%20caught%20budget%20flights%20to%20Italy%20to%20scout%20houses%20for%20me%20in%20Tuscany.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20risky%2C%20but%20I%20bought%20a%20two-bedroom%20house%2C%20located%20in%20a%20hamlet%2030%20miles%20from%20Florence%2C%20pretty%20much%20%26quot%3Bsight%20unseen%2C%26quot%3B%20that%20June.%20Taylor%20had%20shown%20it%20to%20me%20on%20FaceTime%2C%20and%20I%20trusted%20her%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20paid%20120%2C000%20euros%20(around%20%24130%2C000%20USD%20in%202023)%20in%20cash%2C%20and%20saw%20it%20for%20the%20first%20time%20just%20before%20closing%20in%20August.%20It%20was%20a%20beautiful%2C%2019th-century%20stone%20house%20with%20two%20bedrooms%20and%20two%20acres%20of%20terraced%20olive%20groves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227caa9d96-89c6-45ce-9aa4-350f080b0993%5C%22%3EI'm%20far%20from%20fluent%20in%20Italian%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20months%20later%2C%20I%20packed%20my%20belongings%2C%20boarded%20a%20plane%2C%20and%20moved%20into%20the%20small%20two-bedroom%20property.%20It%20was%20the%20best%20decision%20I%20ever%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20residents%20in%20my%20hamlet%20belong%20to%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmultigenerational-living-pros-cons-parents-health-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emulti-generational%20family%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20from%20babies%20up%20to%20great%20grandparents%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they've%20welcomed%20me%20with%20open%20arms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20taught%20me%20how%20to%20take%20care%20of%20my%20olive%20trees%20and%20even%20helped%20me%20with%20my%20first%20harvest%20in%202024.%20I%20speak%20a%20combination%20of%20English%20and%20Italian%20to%20them%2C%20but%20I'm%20far%20from%20fluent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20life%20is%20much%20quieter%20now%20%E2%80%94%20and%20so%20much%20healthier.%20I%20don't%20have%20the%20migraines%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221163%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20group%20of%20six%20women%20standing%20amid%20mountains%20in%20Italy.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e66c97367066d7c296ead9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22872%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESmith%2C%20third%20from%20left%2C%20now%20organizes%20women's%20retreats%20in%20Tuscany.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Angie%20Smith.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20an%20outdoorsy%20person%2C%20and%20because%20I%20live%20in%20the%20mountains%2C%20where%20it's%20cooler%2C%20I%20hike%20a%20lot.%20Physical%20activity%20and%20good%20eating%20have%20helped%20me%20to%20lose%20a%20total%20of%2042%20pounds%20in%20two-and-a-half%20years.%20I'm%20down%20from%20an%20extra%20large%20to%20a%20medium.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20food%20tastes%20so%20much%20better%20than%20American%20food%2C%20mostly%20because%20it's%20mostly%20free%20of%20preservatives.%20So%20many%20things%20I%20ate%20in%20the%20US%20inflamed%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20visited%20my%20family%20in%20the%20US%2C%20my%20face%20got%20puffy%2C%20and%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2