2132.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20WORLD%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fdid-donald-trumps-social-media-posts-derail-fragile-us-iran-peace-talks%2Farticleshow%2F130412132.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Musk%20vs%20Altman%20trial%20is%20fast%20approaching.%20The%20stakes%20are%20high%20for%20OpenAI%20and%20its%20CEO.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sam%20Altman%2C%20CEO%20of%20OpenAI%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e283e23fecbb42897a12f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESam%20Altman%20cofounded%20OpenAI%20years%20ago%20along%20with%20Musk%20and%20others.%20The%20AI%20company's%20shift%20from%20a%20nonprofit%20to%20a%20for-profit%20entity%20is%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20Tesla%20CEO's%20lawsuit.%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FBloomberg%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETech%20titans%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20Sam%20Altman%20will%20face%20off%20in%20court%20starting%20April%2027.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMusk%20has%20accused%20Altman%20of%20deceiving%20him%20into%20donating%20%2438%20million%20to%20OpenAI%2C%20which%20he%20helped%20cofound.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThere's%20a%20lot%20at%20stake%20for%20the%20defendants%2C%20including%20Altman%2C%20OpenAI%2C%20and%20even%20its%20major%20investor%2C%20Microsoft.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWas%20OpenAI%20built%20on%20a%20lie%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20could%20a%20jury%20sympathetic%20to%20that%20claim%20force%20it%20to%20undergo%20yet%20another%20dramatic%20transformation%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%20this%20month%2C%20Elon%20Musk%20will%20ask%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjudge-rejects-sam-altman-efforts-toss-elon-musk-case-openai-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOakland%20federal%20jury%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20decide%20whether%20his%20fellow%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOpenAI%20cofounders%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faltman-molotov-attack-suspect-had-an-anti-ai-doc-feds-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESam%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Greg%20Brockman%2C%20deceived%20him%20into%20donating%20%2438%20million%20to%20the%20AI%20company%20by%20promising%20it%20would%20remain%20a%20nonprofit%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20humanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20allowing%20the%20case%20to%20go%20to%20trial%2C%20the%20judge%20cited%2C%20among%20other%20evidence%2C%20an%20exhibit%20containing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-sam-altman-lawsuit-unsealed-documents-top-takeaways-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBrockman's%20private%20musings%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20nonprofit%20before%20Musk%20resigned%20from%20its%20board%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3Bcan't%20see%20us%20turning%20this%20into%20a%20for-profit%20without%20a%20very%20nasty%20fight%2C%26quot%3B%20Brockman%20wrote%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20his%20story%20will%20correctly%20be%20that%20we%20weren't%20honest%20with%20him%20in%20the%20end%20about%20still%20wanting%20to%20do%20the%20for%20profit%20just%20without%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20exhibit%20also%20shows%20Brockman%20saying%20it%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bmorally%20bankrupt%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3Bsteal%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20from%20Musk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20battle%20of%20the%20titans%20is%20set%20to%20kick%20off%20with%20jury%20selection%20on%20April%2027%2C%20marking%20the%20culmination%20of%20a%20feud%20that%20has%20long%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhistory-of-elon-musk-and-sam-altman-relationship-feuds-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Espilled%20outside%20the%20courtroom%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20OpenAI%20asked%20the%20attorneys%20general%20of%20California%20and%20Delaware%20to%20probe%20%26quot%3Banti-competitive%20behavior%26quot%3B%20by%20Musk%2C%20who%20runs%20rival%20AI%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FX.AI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ExAI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20latest%20twist%2C%20Musk%20has%20asked%20the%20Oakland%20federal%20judge%20overseeing%20the%20case%20to%20consider%20removing%20Altman%20as%20an%20officer%20of%20the%20for-profit%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eif%20the%20jury%20finds%20him%20liable%2C%20among%20other%20potential%20remedies.%20The%20judge%20will%20review%20potential%20remedies%20after%20the%20jury%20decides%20on%20the%20liability%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20what's%20at%20stake%20for%20the%20key%20players%20in%20this%20legal%20battle%3F%20We%20compiled%20a%20list%20of%20potential%20consequences%20for%20OpenAI%2C%20Altman%2C%20Musk%2C%20and%20more%20as%20the%20trial%20nears.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2222867231-0562-4646-85a9-d2cfb0eec127%5C%22%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20case%20is%20OpenAI's%202025%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-one-step-closer-becoming-profit-company-report-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etransition%20to%20a%20for-profit%20entity.%3C%2Fa%3E%20If%20he%20wins%2C%20Musk%20wants%20OpenAI%2C%20now%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-profitability-analyst-investor-opinions-funding-ipo-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evalued%20at%20over%20%24800%20billion%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20returned%20to%20a%20nonprofit%20entity.%20He's%20also%20asking%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmusk-seeks-134-billion-legal-battle-over-open-ai-microsoft-2026-01%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebillions%20in%20disgorgement%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20returned%20to%20the%20nonprofit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20forced%20to%20revert%20to%20a%20nonprofit%2C%20OpenAI%20could%20face%20fundraising%20headaches%20as%20it%20lays%20the%20groundwork%20for%20a%20possible%20IPO%2C%20which%20could%20happen%20as%20soon%20as%20this%20year.%20The%20AI%20company%20has%20been%20on%20a%20seemingly%20never-ending%20quest%20to%20raise%20the%20capital%20necessary%20to%20train%20and%20launch%20more%20advanced%20LLMs%2C%20and%20previously%20faced%20investor%20pressure%20to%20restructure%20into%20a%20more%20traditional%20for-profit%20entity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b66cc6cb-f037-4cb3-bee8-2059a1e85382%5C%22%3ESam%20Altman%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20is%20seeking%20to%20have%20Altman%20removed%20as%20a%20director%20of%20the%20nonprofit%20and%20as%20an%20officer%20of%20the%20for-profit.%20He%20also%20wants%20to%20strip%20Altman%20of%20his%20equity%20in%20the%20company%2C%20which%20could%20limit%20Altman's%20ability%20to%20profit%20if%20OpenAI%20goes%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20the%20judge%20would%20agree%20with%20Musk's%20request%20to%20remove%20Altman%20is%20another%20question.%20On%20Friday%2C%20the%20judge%20questioned%20whether%20some%20of%20Musk's%20remedy%20requests%20were%20within%20her%20powers.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EShe%20said%20she%20will%20consider%20Musk's%20demands%20after%20the%20jury%20decides%20on%20the%20liability%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20could%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-shock-firing-from-openai-just-became-bigger-mystery-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereignite%20questions%20about%20Altman's%20leadership%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhich%20were%20thrust%20into%20the%20limelight%20when%20he%20was%20briefly%20fired%20by%20the%20board%20in%202023.%20Musk's%20lawyers%20are%20expected%20to%20call%20to%20the%20witness%20stand%20former%20board%20members%20who%20voted%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-sam-altman-new-yorker-profile-character-information-cfo-policy-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAltman%20to%20be%20fired%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20saying%20he%20fostered%20a%20%26quot%3Btoxic%20culture%20of%20lying%2C%26quot%3B%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eincluding%20potentially%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-openai-board-members-challenge-self-governance-sam-altman-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETasha%20McCauley.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegardless%20of%20the%20legal%20outcome%2C%20testimony%20about%20Altman%20could%20prove%20bruising%2C%20especially%20as%20it%20comes%20hot%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20Ronan%20Farrow's%20New%20Yorker%20investigation%20questioning%20if%20the%20CEO%20could%20be%20trusted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222630ece6-280a-4395-906d-4677bfb18762%5C%22%3EGreg%20Brockman%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20is%20also%20seeking%20to%20have%20Brockman%20removed%20as%20an%20officer%20of%20OpenAI%20and%20stripped%20of%20his%20equity%20in%20the%20company.%20Brockman%20is%20currently%20president%20of%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20Altman%2C%20Brockman%20can%20also%20expect%20to%20be%20confronted%20with%20potentially%20uncomfortable%20evidence%20at%20trial%2C%20including%20more%20of%20his%20diary%20entries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c598e12f-9851-4d47-bdcd-fd1206fd1f5e%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20claims%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-microsoft-openai-lawsuit-amended-monopoly-ai-sam-altman-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhich%20invested%20%241%20billion%20in%20OpenAI%20in%202019%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-microsoft-openai-lawsuit-amended-monopoly-ai-sam-altman-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eaided%20and%20abetted%3C%2Fa%3E%20OpenAI's%20breach%20of%20his%20charitable%20donations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20effort%20to%20force%20OpenAI%20to%20revert%20to%20a%20nonprofit%20could%20dismantle%20the%20current%20commercial%20structure%20between%20OpenAI%20and%20Microsoft%2C%20which%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fo