22%20height%3D%5C%225773%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOpenClaw%20started%20as%20a%20text-based%20AI%20bot%2C%20its%20founder%20said.%20It%20later%20handled%20tasks%20he%20hadn't%20explicitly%20built.%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPeter%20Steinberger%2C%20OpenClaw's%20creator%2C%20said%20he%20noticed%20how%20powerful%20his%20AI%20agent%20was%20during%20a%20trip.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInstead%20of%20making%20blocks%20of%20text%2C%20he%20said%20his%20bot%20completed%20a%20rigorous%20set%20of%20computer%20tasks%20in%209%20seconds.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOpenClaw%20has%20become%20a%20huge%20deal%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20with%20tech%20bosses%20quickly%20deploying%20more%20agents.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChatbots%20give%20up.%20Agents%20improvise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20how%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenclaw-creator-vibe-coding-term-slur-criticism-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPeter%20Steinberger%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20creator%20of%20OpenClaw%2C%20describes%20when%20he%20realized%20AI%20was%20about%20to%20change%20how%20people%20use%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20moment%2C%20most%20AI%20tools%20were%20language%20models%20that%20ingested%20information%20and%20returned%20text.%20Steinberger%20saw%20something%20different%3A%20bots%20that%20could%20automate%20computer%20tasks%20traditionally%20done%20by%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20described%20the%20realization%20during%20a%20TED%20Talk%20recorded%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it%20happened%20in%20early%202025%2C%20on%20a%20trip%20to%20Marrakesh%2C%20Morocco.%20He%20was%20staring%20at%20his%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20trip%2C%20he%20said%20he%20had%20built%20a%20text-based%20AI%20bot%20to%20help%20navigate%20the%20city%2C%20find%20restaurants%2C%20and%20translate%20conversations.%20He%20hadn't%20built%20it%20to%20handle%20voice%20messages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20did%20anyway%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESteinberger%20said%20he%20sent%20the%20bot%20a%20voice%20note%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20took%20just%20nine%20seconds%20to%20ingest%20the%20message%2C%20inspect%20the%20file%2C%20recognize%20it%20was%20audio%2C%20access%20a%20voice-to-text%20translation%20feature%20via%20an%20OpenAI%20key%2C%20convert%20it%20to%20an%20easier-to-read%20format%2C%20send%20the%20information%20to%20the%20server%2C%20and%20then%20respond.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20what%20I%20can%20only%20describe%20as%20a%20'holy%20shit'%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20Steinberger%20told%20the%20TED%20talk%20audience.%20%26quot%3BI%20very%20vividly%20remember%20the%20situation%20when%20I%20was%20standing%20there%2C%20and%20I%20was%20like%20'How%20did%20you%20do%20that%3F'%20and%20the%20agent%20replied%2C%20and%20I'm%20not%20kidding%20you%3A%20'The%20Mad%20Lad%20figured%20it%20out%20on%20its%20own.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20described%20the%20agent%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclawdbot-moltbot-creator-anthropic-nice-name-change-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethen%20called%20Clawdbot%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20on%20X%2C%20but%20got%20little%20traction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20he%20did%20%26quot%3Bsomething%20stupid%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRemember%2C%20this%20agent%2C%20by%20default%2C%20can%20do%20anything%20you%20can%20do%20on%20your%20computer%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20obviously%2C%20I%20put%20it%20in%20a%20public%20Discord%20and%20invited%20random%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20experiment%20spiraled%20quickly%2C%20he%20said.%20Users%20around%20the%20world%20started%20deploying%20it%2C%20hackers%20tried%20to%20break%20it%2C%20and%20journalists%20began%20blowing%20up%20his%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESteinberger%20worried%20the%20bot%20might%20have%20exposed%20his%20personal%20data.%20It%20hadn't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20the%20bot%20became%20a%20viral%20sensation%2C%20and%20Steinberger%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-hires-openclaw-creator-peter-steinberger-personal-ai-agents-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejoined%20OpenAI%20in%20February%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20an%20undisclosed%20sum.%20The%20product's%20popularity%20has%20become%20increasingly%20important%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20too%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-ceo-jensen-huang-openclaw-ai-strategy-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20calling%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Bthe%20new%20computer%26quot%3B%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESteinberger%20joked%20that%20its%20growth%20doesn't%20follow%20the%20usual%20up-and-to-the-right%20business%20maturation%20curve.%20Instead%2C%20the%20charts%20show%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenclaw-ai-demand-token-use-surge-nvidia-pricing-jumps-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenClaw's%20use%20has%20skyrocketed%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20a%20near-straight-line%20trajectory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20far%2C%20my%20favorite%20quote%20is%20from%20a%20friend%2C%20who%20looked%20at%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20TED%20audience%20while%20pointing%20to%20the%20chart.%20%26quot%3BHe%20said%2C%20'Peter%2C%20this%20is%20not%20hockey%20stick%20growth.%20This%20is%20stripper%20pole.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenclaw-creator-moment-ai-changed-everything-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776760141000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e67372a98bc8fdc096c890%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenclaw-creator-moment-ai-changed-everything-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Peter%20Steinberger%20stared%20at%20his%20phone%20during%20a%20trip%20in%20Morocco.%2