3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20California%20judge%20accused%20Amazon%20of%20price-fixing.%3Cp%3EMatthias%20Balk%2Fpicture%20alliance%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20California%20judge%20accused%20Amazon%20of%20price-fixing%20and%20contributing%20to%20the%20affordability%20crisis%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAttorney%20General%20Rob%20Bonta%20said%20Amazon%20asked%20vendors%20like%20Levi's%20to%20pressure%20Walmart%20into%20raising%20prices.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20case%20will%20go%20into%20trial%20in%20January%202027.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20California%20prosecutor%20is%20accusing%20Amazon%20of%20illegally%20raising%20prices%20for%20Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20release%20on%20Monday%2C%20California%20Attorney%20General%20Rob%20Bonta%20said%20that%20Amazon%20is%20price%20fixing%20and%20colluding%20with%20vendors%20and%20retailers%20to%20raise%20costs%20for%20Americans%20beyond%20what%20the%20market%20requires.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmid%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcheap-stuff-economy-prices-american-dream-housing-televisions-tariffs-trump-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecrisis%20of%20affordability%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Amazon%20is%20illegally%20working%20to%20rake%20in%20profits%20by%20making%20sure%20consumers%20have%20nowhere%20else%20to%20turn%20to%20for%20lower%20prices%2C%26quot%3B%20Bonta%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe'll%20see%20them%20in%20court.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20press%20release%2C%20he%20said%20he%20had%20publicly%20released%20evidence%20of%20Amazon's%20price-fixing%2C%20linking%20to%20a%2019-page%20memo.%20Among%20many%20other%20examples%20in%20the%20memo%2C%20Bonta%20wrote%20that%20Amazon%20asked%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flevis-jeans-company-history-timeline-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eapparel%20brand%20Levi's%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-amazon-racing-to-win-retail-ecommerce-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epressure%20Walmart%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0into%20raising%20the%20price%20of%20a%20pair%20of%20its%20khaki%20pants%20from%20about%20%2425%20to%20%2429%20to%20match%20Amazon's%20listing%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20companies%20mentioned%20in%20the%20filing%20include%20Home%20Depot%2C%20Target%2C%20Best%20Buy%2C%20clothing%20brand%20Hanes%2C%20and%20pet%20product%20brand%20Chewy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBonta%20asked%20the%20court%20to%20take%20action%20against%20Amazon%20for%20price%20fixing%20while%20the%20case%20proceeds%20and%20to%20require%20Amazon%20to%20stop%20%26quot%3Bcoercing%20its%20vendors%20to%20serve%20as%20the%20go-between%20with%20its%20competitors.%26quot%3B%20The%20case%20will%20go%20to%20trial%20in%20January%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%2C%20an%20Amazon%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20motion%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Btransparent%20attempt%20to%20distract%20from%20the%20weakness%20of%20its%20case.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20added%20that%20Bonta%20filed%20the%20motion%20more%20than%20three%20years%20after%20filing%20his%20original%20complaint.%20In%202022%2C%20Bonta%20said%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-sues-amazon-accusing-inflating-prices-crushing-competition-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20lawsuit%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Amazon%20coerced%20sellers%20into%20signing%20agreements%20stating%20they%20would%20not%20sell%20their%20goods%20at%20a%20lower%20price%20to%20other%20retailers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmazon%20is%20consistently%20identified%20as%20America's%20lowest-priced%20online%20retailer%2C%20and%20we're%20proud%20of%20the%20low%20prices%20customers%20find%20when%20shopping%20in%20our%20store%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Amazon%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20spokespersons%20for%20Levi's%20and%20Walmart%20declined%20to%20comment%2C%20both%20saying%20they%20were%20not%20parties%20to%20the%20litigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon's%20stock%20price%20is%20up%20about%2043%25%20in%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-amazon-coerced-companies-illegally-raising-prices-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776751919000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e70d1c3fecbb42897a203a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-amazon-coerced-companies-illegally-raising-prices-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Attorney%20General%20Rob%20Bonta%20said%20Amazon%20asked%20vendors%20like%20Levi's%20to%20pressure%20Walmart%20into%20raising%20prices.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abharade%40insider.com%20(Aditi%20Bharade)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-amazon-coerced-companies-illegally-raising-prices-2026-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Riteish%20and%20Genelia's%20son%20steals%20spotlight%20with%20debut%20in%20Raja%20Shivaji%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776751896000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-130409112%2Cimgsize-30454.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Friteish-deshmukh-and-genelia-deshmukhs-10-year-old-son-rahyl-steals-spotlight-with-his-debut-in-raja-shivaji-trailer-watch%2Farticleshow%2F130409112.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F130409112.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERiteish%20Deshmukh's%20Raja%20Shivaji%20trailer%20launched%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20featuring%2010-year-old%20son%20Rahyl's%20deb