%20biosphere%20in%20Uttarakhand.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETogether%2C%20they%20embarked%20on%20a%20challenging%20yet%20rewarding%20journey%2C%20transforming%20former%20agricultural%20land%20into%20a%20flourishing%20forest%20by%20removing%20non-native%20species.%20Their%20goal%20was%20simple%3A%20to%20create%20a%20forest%20exactly%20as%20nature%20intended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20have%20they%20succeeded%2C%20but%20they%E2%80%99ve%20exceeded%20expectations.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20how%20they%20created%20the%20first%20biosphere%20reserve%20in%20India%20where%20the%20carbon%20footprint%20is%20minimal%2C%20time%20seems%20to%20stand%20still%2C%20and%20nature%20takes%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Chowkidar%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20forest%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJai%20completed%20his%20education%20in%20finance%20and%20environmental%20science%20at%20The%20Wharton%20School.%20After%20running%20successful%20businesses%20in%20the%20US%2C%20he%20returned%20to%20India%20in%202010%20to%20continue%20his%20entrepreneurial%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20avid%20runner%2C%20he%20faced%20a%20major%20setback%20in%202013%20when%20he%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20bronchial%20asthma%20while%20training%20for%20a%20marathon.%20This%20diagnosis%2C%20likely%20due%20to%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20severe%20air%20pollution%2C%20ignited%20his%20passion%20for%20environmental%20issues.%20He%20became%20a%20leading%20advocate%20for%20air%20quality%20awareness%2C%20founding%20the%20citizen%E2%80%99s%20movement%20%E2%80%98Our%20Right%20To%20Breathe%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC3Kr8tAy0D0%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC3Kr8tAy0D0%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC3Kr8tAy0D0%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Rajaji%20Raghati%20Biosphere%20(%40rajaji.biosphere)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20efforts%20led%20to%20his%20inclusion%20in%20the%20first%20Air%20Pollution%20Task%20Force%20established%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Government.%20This%20task%20force%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20launching%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20landmark%20odd-even%20traffic%20initiative%20in%202015%2C%20aimed%20at%20reducing%20vehicular%20emissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F251663%2Finnovation-toxic-air-pollution-covid-19-ac-filter-fitting-cost-how-to-buy-online-delhi-information-jai-dhar-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebattle%20against%20air%20pollution%20%3C%2Fa%3Ealso%20inspired%20him%20to%20create%20solutions%20through%20his%20venture%2C%20Nirvana%20Being.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20continued%20to%20advocate%20for%20clean%20air%2C%20he%20came%20to%20the%20realisation%20that%20expecting%20significant%20improvements%20in%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20air%20quality%20within%20his%20lifetime%20was%20unlikely.%20This%20prompted%20him%20to%20seek%20out%20a%20place%20where%20both%20the%20air%20and%20quality%20of%20life%20would%20be%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CI%20always%20dreamt%20of%20being%20a%20chowkidar%20(watchman)%20of%20the%20forests%20in%20India.%20I%20have%20no%20hope%20of%20better%20living%20conditions%20in%20Delhi%20or%20Mumbai.%20The%20air%20is%20toxic%20everywhere.%20I%20want%20to%20improve%20my%20own%20quality%20of%20life%2C%20and%20the%20way%20to%20do%20that%20is%20by%20living%20with%20nature%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jai%20tells%20The%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20Delhi%20resident%2C%20he%20often%20visited%20the%20Rajaji%20Tiger%20Reserve%2C%20where%20he%20developed%20a%20deep%20affection%20for%20the%20wildlife.%20Naturally%2C%20when%20it%20came%20time%20to%20find%20a%20place%20to%20settle%2C%20he%20was%20drawn%20to%20the%20area%20that%20had%20become%20almost%20a%20second%20home%20to%20him%20over%20the%20past%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji3-1724833586.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20biosphere%20is%20a%20result%20of%20Jai's%20search%20for%20clean%20air%20and%20pristine%20nature.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji3-1724833586.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji3-1724833586-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji3-1724833586-500x374.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji3-1724833586-768x575.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji3-1724833586-1536x1150.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji3-1724833586-150x112.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-363167%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221198%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20biosphere%20is%20a%20result%20of%20Jai%E2%80%99s%20search%20for%20clean%20air%20and%20pristine%20nature.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20he%20discovered%20a%20stunning%20piece%20of%20land%20nestled%20between%20the%20Rajaji%20Tiger%20Reserve%20and%20the%20Raghati%20river%2C%20complete%20with%20a%20breathtaking%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F338189%2Fbest-national-park-wildlife-safaris-in-winter-adventure-travel-guide-vacation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E300-metre-wide%20riverbed%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20riverbed%2C%20when%20dry%2C%20serves%20as%20an%20elephant%20corridor%20and%20a%20hub%20of%20wildlife%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20that%20being%20there%20feels%20like%20stepping%20into%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Jungle%20Book%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20where%20you%20can%20watch%20animals%20in%20their%20natural%20habitat%20%E2%80%94%20preying%2C%20drinking%2C%20sleeping%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20biosphere%2C%20he%20explains%2C%20is%20a%20micro-environment.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20zone%20of%20life.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20got%20the%20tiger%20reserve%20next%20to%20us%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20pure%2C%20due%20to%20the%20invasion%20of%20non-native%20species%20like%20eucalyptus%20trees.%20We%20are%20working%20on%20creating%20a%20pure%20environment%2C%20growing%20only%20what%20nature%20intended%20for%20in%20this%20particular%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20chasing%20what%20we%20saw%20in%20that%20movie%20Avatar.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20reconnect%20with%20nature%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20acquiring%20the%20land%2C%20which%20was%20then%20covered%20in%20a%20eucalyptus%20forest%20%E2%80%94%20a%20non-native%20species%20%E2%80%94%20the%20major%20challenge%20was%20rewilding%20it.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20land%20was%20used%20for%20agricultural%20purposes%2C%20it%20had%20been%20flattened%20and%20had%20some%205%2C000%20eucalyptus%20trees.%20These%20trees%20would%20dry%20up%20the%20groundwater%20and%20wetlands%20as%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20belong%20to%20this%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Jai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji4-1724833594.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20biosphere%20was%20created%20through%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%20of%20relentless%20effort.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji4-1724833594.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji4-1724833594-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji4-1724833594-500x374.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji4-1724833594-768x575.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji4-1724833594-1536x1150.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji4-1724833594-150x112.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-363168%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221198%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20biosphere%20was%20created%20through%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%20of%20relentless%20effort.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJai%20and%20Vijay%20surveyed%20the%20nearby%20area%20of%20the%20Rajaji%20Tiger%20Reserve%20and%20National%20Park%20together%2C%20identifying%2062%20native%20tree%20species%20that%20were%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20disappearing.%20The%20project%20began%20with%20the%20collection%20of%20seeds%20and%20the%20painstaking%20process%20of%20planting%20saplings%20of%20these%20endangered%20species.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijay%2C%20who%20has%20been%20in%20the%20rewilding%20and%20wildlife%20restoration%20space%20for%20over%2020%20years%20and%20majorly%20works%20on%20government%20projects%2C%20had%20an%20interesting%20task%20up%20his%20sleeve.%20He%20states%20that%20there%20is%20just%20a%20wall%20that%20separates%20the%20biosphere%20from%20the%20Rajaji%20National%20Park.%20The%20idea%20was%20to%20get%20a%20slice%20of%20Rajaji%20into%20this%20land%2C%20which%20had%20been%20altered%20by%20humans%20for%20their%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20task%20was%20removing%20the%20eucalyptus%20trees.%20The%20second%20task%20was%20creating%20natural%20contours%20that%20existed%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20monsoon%20that%20I%20experienced%20was%20really%20horrifying.%20I%20found%20that%20the%20rainwater%20was%20tapering%20away%20towards%20the%20river.%20Nothing%20was%20being%20retained%20in%20the%20land.%20The%20rain%20was%20taking%20away%20my%20topsoil%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vijay%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20a%20war%20footing%2C%20we%20created%20the%20natural%20contours%20that%20existed%20to%20ensure%20that%20rainwater%20recharges%20our%20land.%20We%20are%20working%20on%20creating%20magic%2C%20every%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20how%20they%20worked%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F345145%2Fforest-officer-saves-trees-in-chhattisgarh-forest-tiger-reserve-from-encroachers-ifs-varun-jain-timber-poaching%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erewilding%20the%20land%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20says%20that%20they%20took%20cues%20from%20the%20forest%20next%20door.%20They%20observed%20the%20forest%20and%20the%20species%20that%20grew%20there%20and%20worked%20on%20recreating%20the%20broken%20linkages%20between%20different%20species%20and%20creating%20an%20interdependence%20between%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-33-1724828441.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22how%20to%20build%20a%20biosphere%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-33-1724828441.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-33-1724828441-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-33-1724828441-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-33-1724828441-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-33-1724828441-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-363141%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20Rajaji%20Raghati%20Biosphere%20is%20rich%20in%20biodiversity%20and%20home%20to%20132%20native%20plant%20species%2C%20including%20many%20that%20had%20all%20but%20disappeared%20from%20the%20region.%20Their%20efforts%20have%20also%20attracted%20a%20diverse%20array%20of%20wildlife%20%E2%80%94%20from%20leopards%20and%20elephants%20to%20an%20abundance%20of%20bird%20species%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20which%20are%20now%20regular%20visitors%20to%20the%20biosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20saplings%20are%20now%20about%20six%20feet%20high%2C%20and%20when%20you%20walk%2C%20you%20feel%20like%20you%E2%80%99re%20walking%20on%20a%20carpet.%20We%20have%20two%20leopards%20and%20elephants%20who%20visit%20regularly.%20Earlier%2C%20when%20they%20would%20come%20down%20the%20corridor%2C%20they%20would%20stop%20and%20show%20signs%20of%20being%20upset.%20Now%2C%20they%20look%20at%20me%20as%20a%20part%20of%20their%20habitat.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20realised%20that%20my%20vision%20of%20coexistence%20is%20coming%20true%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Uttarakhand%20biosphere%20reserve%20operates%20under%20strict%20rules%3A%20vehicles%20and%20plastic%20are%20not%20allowed.%20The%20only%20exception%20is%20a%20single%20electric%20farm%20utility%20vehicle%2C%20which%20also%20serves%20as%20a%20silent%20safari%20vehicle%2C%20ensuring%20minimal%20disturbance%20to%20the%20animals.%20Visitors%20are%20not%20permitted%20to%20bring%20any%20plants%20or%20seeds%20into%20the%20biosphere.%20Every%20effort%20is%20made%20to%20avoid%20activities%20that%20contribute%20to%20a%20carbon%20footprint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20rule%20in%20this%20biosphere%20is%20that%20nature%20comes%20first%2C%20not%20humans%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jai.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20small%20homes%20on%20the%20property%20for%20overnight%20stays%2C%20built%20without%20cement%20and%20bricks%2C%20using%20prefabricated%20construction%20methods.%20Jai%20emphasises%20that%20this%20is%20not%20an%20eco-tourism%20spot%20but%20rather%20a%20model%20intended%20to%20inspire%20others%20who%20wish%20to%20rewild%20their%20own%20spaces.%20He%20has%20also%20written%20a%20white%20paper%20on%20the%20subject%20to%20raise%20awareness%20and%20motivate%20others%20to%20take%20similar%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20already%20feel%20like%20the%20richest%20person%20on%20the%20planet.%20I%20have%20created%20more%20wealth%20over%20the%20past%202.5%20years%20than%20in%20the%2050%20years%20before%20that.%20One%20must%20realise%20that%20richness%20is%20not%20in%20our%2030%2C000%20sq%20ft%20mansions%20and%20apartments%20in%20cities.%20The%20richness%20lies%20in%20mental%20peace%2C%20which%20I%E2%80%99ve%20found.%20Most%20days%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20even%20walking%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20levitating%20in%20the%20biosphere%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijay%20too%20adds%20that%20he%20has%20received%20calls%20from%20people%20across%20the%20country%20interested%20in%20replicating%20this%20initiative.%20The%20message%20the%20duo%20want%20to%20give%20out%20is%20clear%20as%20day%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CLet%E2%80%99s%20go%20back%20to%20the%20simpler%20things%20and%20reconnect%20with%20nature.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EImages%20Courtesy%20Jai%20Dhar%20Gupta%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757331000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji2-1724829336.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D498044%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Inspired%20by%20the%20movie%20Avatar%2C%20environmentalist%20and%20clean%20air%20activist%20Jai%20Dhar%20Gupta%20turned%2032%20acres%20near%20Uttarakhand's%20Rajaji%20National%20Park%20into%20a%20biosphere.%20With%20the%20help%20of%20expert%20Vijay%20Dhasmana%2C%20he%20revived%20the%20land%2C%20bringing%20back%20native%20plants%20and%20wildlife.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F498044%2Fprivate-biosphere-rajaji-uttarakhand-rewilding%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98I%20Turned%20My%20Life%20Around%E2%80%99%3A%20How%20a%20Farmer%20Built%20An%20Aloe%20Vera%20Business%20With%20a%20Turnover%20of%20Rs%203.5%20Cr%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20interviews%20and%20reporting%20for%20this%20story%20were%20conducted%20in%20August%202024.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20drought-prone%20Satara%20district%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20farmers%20were%20largely%20dependent%20on%20rain%20for%20irrigation.%20Often%20without%20any%20regular%20irrigation%20facilities%2C%20they%20would%20be%20forced%20to%20leave%20their%20crops%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%20two%20decades%20back%2C%20farmers%20in%20Padali%20village%20were%20fooled%20into%20taking%20up%20aloe%20vera%20farming%20by%20claiming%20the%20crop%20would%20ensure%20good%20yield%20in%20the%20rainfed%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A497045%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Ftbi-showcase%2F%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20businessman%20had%20come%20to%20our%20village%20and%20advertised%20about%20aloe%20vera%20farming.%20He%20distributed%20pamphlets%20wherein%20farmers%20had%20stacks%20of%20money%20on%20one%20hand%20and%20aloe%20vera%20plants%20on%20the%20other.%20It%20mentioned%20%E2%80%98Aloe%20vera%20%3Cem%3Elagaiye%20aur%20lakho%20kamaiye%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3E(grow%20aloe%20vera%20and%20earn%20in%20lakhs)%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20farmer%20Hrushikesh%20Jayasing%20Dhane%20(44).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInfluenced%20by%20this%2C%20several%20farmers%20bought%20thousands%20of%20plants%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F301751%2Fbusiness-school-grad-leaves-london-to-organic-farm-help-farmers-earn-jaivik-jeevan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplanted%20them%20on%20their%20barren%20lands%20%3C%2Fa%3Eimagining%20themselves%20as%20the%20man%20in%20the%20advertisement.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20curious%20about%20the%20crop%2C%20but%20I%20also%20had%20doubts%20about%20it.%20So%20I%20went%20to%20the%20office%20and%20enquired%20about%20the%20market.%20I%20asked%20to%20be%20told%20about%2010%20such%20farmers%20who%20earned%20lakhs%20from%20aloe%20vera.%20The%20local%20officials%20got%20angry%20and%20threw%20me%20out%20of%20the%20office%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20harvesting%20period%20came%20in%2C%20Hrushikesh%20says%2C%20the%20businessman%20had%20run%20away.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20all%20a%20fraud.%20I%20saw%20farmers%20crying.%20They%20did%20not%20have%20any%20strategy%20to%20market%20the%20crop%2C%20so%20they%20started%20clearing%20their%20fields%20and%20some%20threw%20them%20on%20roads%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20Interestingly%2C%20Hrushikesh%20picked%20the%20discarded%20aloe%20vera%20plants%20and%20planted%20them%20in%20his%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20decision%20took%20him%20on%20a%20path%20which%20led%20him%20to%20establishing%2C%20what%20is%20today%2C%20a%20multi-crore%20company!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hrushikesh%20started%20by%20planting%204%2C000%20discarded%20aloe%20vera%20plants%20on%20his%20field.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360102%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHrushikesh%20started%20by%20planting%204%2C000%20discarded%20aloe%20vera%20plants%20in%20his%20field.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELife%20in%20the%20drought-prone%20village%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaised%20in%20a%20humble%20family%20of%20farmers%2C%20Hrushikesh%20owned%20eight%20acres%20of%20land%20in%20Padali%20village.%20The%20family%20had%20traditionally%20been%20growing%20crops%20like%20paddy%2C%20pearl%20millet%2C%20sorghum%2C%20and%20wheat.%20Despite%20toiling%20hard%20on%20the%20field%2C%20they%20would%20not%20get%20sufficient%20output.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20entirely%20dependent%20on%20rainwater%20for%20irrigation%2C%20as%20the%20nearest%20river%20was%20four%20kilometres%20away%2C%20and%20we%20lacked%20the%20necessary%20machinery%20for%20lift%20irrigation.%20Consequently%2C%20our%20crops%20often%20dried%20up.%20Despite%20having%20a%20good%20amount%20of%20land%2C%20it%20remained%20barren%20for%20much%20of%20the%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20of%20four%20was%20dependent%20on%20their%20father%E2%80%99s%20monthly%20salary%20of%20Rs%202%2C000%20and%20lived%20in%20a%20small%20%3Cem%3Ekachha%3C%2Fem%3E%20(mud)%20home.%20Such%20was%20the%20financial%20status%20of%20the%20family%20that%20they%20survived%20on%20low-quality%20sorghum%20%3Cem%3Echapatis%3C%2Fem%3E%20(flatbread)%2C%20and%20occasionally%2C%20vegetables.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20Class%2010%2C%20Hrushikesh%20never%20wore%20a%20pair%20of%20slippers.%20At%2020%2C%20to%20supplement%20his%20family%20income%20and%20support%20his%20higher%20education%2C%20he%20started%20working%20for%20a%20marketing%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20part%20of%20my%20job%2C%20I%20would%20receive%20Rs%203%2C500%20a%20month%20if%20I%20met%20the%20target%20of%20promoting%20Rs%201%20lakh%20in%20sales.%20This%20income%20was%20not%20fixed%2C%20and%20they%20required%20me%20to%20relocate%2025%20km%20away.%20I%20attempted%20to%20do%20this%20work%20for%20three%20to%20four%20months%2C%20but%20it%20became%20unsustainable%20because%20I%20also%20had%20to%20manage%20my%20field%20responsibilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-3-1723014113.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hrushikesh%20says%20farmers%20can%20earn%20good%20profits%20if%20they%20make%20products%20from%20aloe%20vera%20like%20juice%2C%20soaps%2C%20fertilisers.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-3-1723014113.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-3-1723014113-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-3-1723014113-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-3-1723014113-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-3-1723014113-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360104%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHrushikesh%20says%20farmers%20can%20earn%20good%20profits%20if%20they%20make%20products%20from%20aloe%20vera%20like%20juice%2C%20soaps%2C%20and%20fertilisers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20run%20a%20business%20from%20the%20village%2C%20he%20started%20a%20nursery%20by%20selling%20moringa%20and%20mango%20saplings.%20However%2C%20this%20business%20would%20peak%20only%20during%20the%20monsoon.%20Gradually%2C%20he%20started%20selling%20fertilisers%20to%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20turning%20point%20came%20into%20his%20life%20in%202007%20when%20farmers%20were%20throwing%20aloe%20vera%20plants%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETurned%20adversity%20into%20opportunity%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHrushikesh%20planted%204%2C000%20discarded%20aloe%20vera%20plants%20between%20mango%20and%20%3Cem%3Eamla%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Indian%20gooseberry)%20trees.%20%E2%80%9CI%20thought%20there%20was%20no%20harm%20in%20growing%20aloe%20vera%20on%20my%20farm%2C%20even%20if%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20generate%20immediate%20income.%20I%20knew%20that%20aloe%20vera%20could%20work%20wonders%20as%20a%20termite%20repellent%20and%20would%20help%20protect%20my%20mango%20trees%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20graduate%2C%20who%20holds%20a%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20horticulture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20offline%20exhibitions%20organised%20in%20Satara%2C%20he%20often%20came%20across%20small%20entrepreneurs%20selling%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F237401%2Fman-earns-lakhs-aloe-vera-organic-online-fresh-products-self-help-groups-inspiring-rural-development-meghalaya-rongram-india-ana79%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealoe%20vera%20products%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CInspired%20by%20the%20idea%2C%20I%20started%20preparing%20products%20like%20soaps%2C%20shampoos%2C%20and%20aloe%20vera%20juice.%20But%20this%20did%20not%20bring%20me%20good%20profits%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20his%20expertise%20in%20horticulture%2C%20he%20went%20on%20to%20utilise%20aloe%20vera%20to%20make%20natural%20pesticides%2C%20herbal%20spreader%2C%20and%20plant%20growth%20promoter.%20%E2%80%9CInsect%20thrips%20damage%20the%20buds%20and%20leaves%20of%20crops.%20I%20once%20mixed%20aloe%20vera%20with%20fish%20oil%20and%20sprayed%20it%20on%20crops.%20Pests%20and%20animals%20dislike%20it%20because%20of%20its%20bitter%20taste.%20I%20found%20this%20to%20be%20an%20effective%20pest%20repellent%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-1-1723014094.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hrushikesh%20utilises%20aloe%20vera%20to%20make%20natural%20pesticides%2C%20herbal%20spreader%2C%20and%20plant%20growth%20promoter.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-1-1723014094.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-1-1723014094-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-1-1723014094-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-1-1723014094-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-1-1723014094-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360103%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHrushikesh%20uses%20aloe%20vera%20to%20make%20natural%20pesticides%2C%20herbal%20spreaders%2C%20and%20plant%20growth%20promoters.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CPlants%20like%20bananas%20naturally%20avert%20water%20on%20its%20surface.%20It%20becomes%20difficult%20for%20farmers%20to%20spray%20pesticides%20on%20their%20leaves.%20Spraying%20aloe%20vera%20spreader%20helps%20spread%20pesticide%20throughout%20the%20length%20of%20the%20plant.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20Hrushikesh%20started%20commercialising%20these%20products%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20friends%20he%20made%20from%20marketing%20jobs.%20Today%2C%20he%20manufactures%20an%20average%20of%208%2C000%20litres%20of%20products%20from%20his%20aloe%20vera%20farm%2C%20now%20expanded%20to%20two%20acres%20of%20land.%20With%20this%2C%20he%20has%20been%20able%20to%20clock%20an%20annual%20turnover%20of%20Rs%203.5%20crore%2C%20of%20which%2C%20his%20profit%20margin%20is%2030%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20feat%20did%20not%20come%20easy%20to%20Hrushikesh.%20Initially%2C%20his%20decision%20to%20plant%20aloe%20vera%20on%20the%20field%20was%20greatly%20opposed%20by%20his%20in-laws.%20His%20wife%20Madhura%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20newly%20married%20then%2C%20and%20I%20did%20not%20have%20much%20idea%20about%20the%20crop.%20My%20parents%20were%20against%20this%20decision.%20They%20believed%20aloe%20vera%20could%20bring%20us%20misery%20as%20the%20plant%20has%20thorns.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20my%20husband%20proved%20them%20wrong.%20Now%2C%20my%20parents%20often%20take%20aloe%20vera%20from%20our%20field%20to%20apply%20on%20their%20hair%20and%20drink%20its%20juice%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20at%20his%20success%2C%20Hrushikesh%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20started%20planting%20aloe%20vera%2C%20I%20was%20told%20that%20if%20you%20plant%20thorny%20plants%2C%20it%20will%20bring%20bad%20luck.%20Back%20then%2C%20I%20lived%20in%20a%C2%A0kachha%C2%A0house%2C%20but%20today%2C%20I%20have%20built%20a%20two-storey%20home%20in%20my%20village%20and%20we%20travel%20in%20a%20Fortuner%20car!%20All%20this%20became%20possible%20only%20because%20of%20growing%20aloe%20vera.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20farmers%20should%20not%20be%20swayed%20solely%20by%20potential%20earnings.%20It%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20understand%20that%20significant%20profits%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F296876%2Frajasthan-tea-seller-earns-lakhs-from-aloe-vera-farming-juice-products%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealoe%20vera%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20more%20likely%20if%20we%20focus%20on%20producing%20products%20and%20expanding%20the%20operation%20accordingly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757313000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D497045%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20drought-prone%20Satara%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20farmer%20Hrushikesh%20Jayasing%20Dhane%20turned%20adversity%20into%20success%20by%20making%20aloe%20vera%20products%20like%20soaps%2C%20shampoos%2C%20and%20juices%2C%20building%20a%20multi-crore%20business.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F497045%2Faloe-vera-farming-success-story-satara-farmer-hrushikesh-dhane-maharashtra%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20How%20a%20Snake%20Rescue%20in%20a%20Delhi%20School%20Taught%20a%20Lesson%20in%20Coexistence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F458137%2Fhimachal-monsoon-travel-guide%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHeavy%20monsoon%20rains%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20drenched%20South%20Delhi%20when%20panic%20rippled%20through%20a%20school%20campus.%20In%20the%20storeroom%20of%20Kendriya%20Vidyalaya%2C%20NMR%2C%20staff%20stumbled%20upon%20an%20unexpected%20guest%20%E2%80%94%20a%20large%20snake%20coiled%20in%20the%20corner.%20Instead%20of%20fear%20turning%20into%20chaos%2C%20what%20followed%20was%20a%20lesson%20in%20calm%20and%20coexistence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActing%20swiftly%2C%20Principal%20Chandan